{"type":"message","id":"f3fd964a","parentId":"c4e41681","timestamp":"2026-03-29T04:47:43.044Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sun 2026-03-29 12:47 GMT+8] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: 搜索企业数字化转型、智能安防、网络系统集成、IT运维服务等道简网络相关行业的最新动态，整理3-5条关键信息，保存到 /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md。搜索2026年3月的最新信息。"}],"timestamp":1774759663041}}
